subject: Skiing
Alpine Skiing
World Cup (Skiing)
lead_paragraph: Frida Hansdotter of Sweden dominated a World Cup night slalom in Flachau. Tina Maze of Slovenia was 0.61 of a second behind in second, and the American Mikaela Shiffrin was third.
